## Build VM — optional smoke (no printer)

```powershell
.\artifacts\app\EventPlatform.PrintRelay.exe
```

Use for tray/UI smoke only. Do not use build VM output for physical dimension sign-off.

---

## If build VM says “Already up to date” but behaviour is old

- Confirm branch: `git branch --show-current` → must match agent’s branch
- Confirm remote: `git log -1 --oneline` vs agent’s SHA
- Agent may not have pushed yet — ask for push or check GitHub
